        <br />
        <p>Are you passionate about immigrant rights and fighting unjust deportation? Do you want to be able to connect immigrants in your community to free legal representation through the <a href="https://equitycorps.org/" target="blank">Equity Corps program</a>?</p>
        <p>Pueblo Unido has subcontracted with <a href="https://innovationlawlab.org/" target="blank">Innovation Law Lab</a> to provide free trainings to people interested in becoming volunteer Community Navigators.</p>
        <p>We invite you to join us for our next free Equity Corps Navigator Training opportunities led by Pueblo Unido PDX and hosted by <a href="https://centrolatinoamericano.org/" target="blank">Centro Latino Americano</a> and <a href="https://ccsww.org/" target="blank">Catholic Community Services</a>.</p> 
