          </ul>
        <p>Sign up for the training <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFyaj6-bw8sqdHTau2adwmQ-h7en4GbhQbndogZNV-sE8nsA/viewform?usp=sf_link" target="blank">here</a>, or use the form below.</p>
        <br />
      </div>
